---
title: Pesto Mozzarella Flatbreads with Garden Salad
description: Juicy baby tomatoes, rich pesto and tender bell peppers top these garden-fresh flatbreads. A flourish of mozzarella and a sprinkling of chili flakes add a creamy, spicy kick to this delectable dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pains-plats-au-pesto-et-a-la-mozzarella-6891ec08.jpg
